# Glow Guide Project Rule

This is the Glow Guide project - a skincare recommendation website for Indian women.

Before doing ANYTHING in this project, always read:
1. `ARCHITECT.md` - project structure, tech stack, pages, database schema
2. `UI_RULES.md` - all design decisions, colors, fonts, animations
3. `AI_PROMPT.md` - only when working on the AI recommendation engine

## Hard Rules

- Never use fonts other than Cormorant Garamond and DM Sans.
- Always write TypeScript, never plain JavaScript.
- Always mobile first.
- Every UI decision must feel warm, feminine, luxurious.
- The user is an Indian woman aged 18-35. Design for her.
